{"tid":180350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劏房似監倉 逾九成住戶受壓","createTime":"2017-03-31T01:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T04:25:18.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c18113d4e49d9d3c32f7b5174c5b69e4b044b46c","tid":180350,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://dadazim.com/journal/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Photo-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdadazim.com%2Fjournal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2FPhoto-4.jpg&h=0e1c6150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】居於環境惡劣狹小的地方或影響精神健康。一項以居於劏房、天台屋及分租床位的市民為對象的調查發現，逾九成受訪者認為住屋問題是主要的壓力來源、逾六成曾感情緒低落、逾五成曾感緊張及焦慮、七成因居住環境太熱或嘈雜，導致睡眠質素欠佳、四成更失眠和健康變差。八成劏房家長更因此擔心子女的健康及個人發展，有人形容劏房的環境只有四面牆，感覺像坐監，覺得小朋友很可憐，促請政府加強支援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/495000/499390/sksinn20130811103_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F495000%2F499390%2Fsksinn20130811103_630_1024.jpg&h=d7ecefd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/61679/xlarge/1c71c00ae66e50544e1187eeaf29bb75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F61679%2Fxlarge%2F1c71c00ae66e50544e1187eeaf29bb75.jpg&h=86ac4464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倡增精神健康服務支援<br />\n聯盟建議政府針對不適切居所林立的舊區，增加精神健康綜合社區中心或相關服務的撥款，支援廿四小時輔導熱線，為低收入人士特別是劏房住戶提供情緒支援，同時訂定全新的租務管制政策，限制劏房租金上調幅度；政府亦應重推「N無津貼」，紓緩基層市民承受的租金壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170331/00176_064.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170331%2F00176_064.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0bf30415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170331/00176_064.html</a>"},{"pid":"51ce1bc59410f6a8eb5919991ef3648147e2085d","tid":180350,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa441b504feeb005e0c272817b0287c111fa6e4","tid":180350,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"http://dadazim.com/journal/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Photo-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdadazim.com%2Fjournal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2FPhoto-4.jpg&h=0e1c6150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官商勾結問題<br />\nBtw, 呢張相影得好好，夠晒壓迫感"},{"pid":"3a731e28f0031bb2e5ada7269011bcb1b4450501","tid":180350,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"最慘係你肯去住<br />\n成班人去政府總部，唔信政府唔做野"}]}